<div class="container">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div id="comments-14">
        
            <article id="comment-413">
              <time datetime="2010-10-04">October 04, 2010</time>
              <p>i love this restaurant is one of the best in london, i just have one thing to say, some dishes have been removed from the menu such as chilly prawn and home made lemonade and i dont see why it should be taken out of the menu other wise i love this restaurant</p>
              <p class="author">From Mohammed</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-409">
              <time datetime="2010-10-02">October 02, 2010</time>
              <p>Hi there!
<br />Have lunch in Busaba Soho location today and loved the food! Thanks a lot! Hugz from Madeira Island! :D Hope to come back soon! 
<br />:D</p>
              <p class="author">From Filipe</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-405">
              <time datetime="2010-10-02">October 02, 2010</time>
              <p>Just stumbled upon the Panton street restaurant. Absolutely gorgeous cooking, great selection and lovely presentation.
<br />Amazing sides of Pandan Chicken and Thai Calamari! Best part was the not too damaging bill at the end. Perfect! 5*</p>
              <p class="author">From Raoul</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-397">
              <time datetime="2010-09-30">September 30, 2010</time>
              <p>I had gone in for a quiet working lunch with one of my managers and the restaurant was very quiet, our waitress was very friendly and the food was delicious. The only criticism would be that when it was time to pay there was no facility to leave a tip on my card which I would have liked to do as despite more tables coming in both waitresses were very friendly and attentive. </p>
              <p class="author">From M Yassin</p>
    
            </article>


            <article id="comment-393">
              <time datetime="2010-09-29">September 29, 2010</time>
              <p>We both love Busaba so much!! Actually it's to a ridiculous extent! I hope they open a restaurant in Brighton (Busaba would go down a storm) &amp; add a desert or two in the not too distant future...</p>
              <p class="author">From Sandie & Paul</p>
    
            </article>

